Guest Handbook

Quick, practical info for your stay (mobile-friendly).

Welcome

Thank you for choosing to stay here.

This space is calm, simple, and easy a place to slow down, settle in, and enjoy a quieter rhythm while youre here on the Sunshine Coast.

Whether youre staying for work, rest, or a short escape, we hope the space feels comfortable and thoughtful from the moment you arrive. If you need anything during your stay, were close by and always happy to help.

Your Stay

This upstairs retreat includes:

  • A private bedroom with queen bed
  • Ensuite bathroom
  • Fresh linen and bath towels
  • Basic toiletries
  • Tea and coffee provisions
  • Smart TV
  • WiFi access
  • Storage space for your belongings
  • Outdoor area / balcony
  • Openplan living area
  • (Guest use: all upstairs areas + lockup garage)
  • Open plan living area
  • Outdoor area

For guest use (i.e., all upstairs areas and lock-up garage).

WiFi

Please refer to the WiFi QR code on the kitchen counter or beside the TV.

If you have any issues connecting, just let us know.

CheckIn & CheckOut

Checkin: from 3:00 pm
Checkout: by 11:00 am

If you need flexibility around these times, feel free to ask well help where we can.

A Few Things to Know

To keep the space feeling calm and comfortable for everyone, there are just a few things we ask you to be mindful of during your stay:

  • Quiet hours are between 10:00 pm and 6:00 am
  • This is a smokefree and vapefree home
  • Please only use the areas outlined for guest use
  • If youre unsure about anything, just ask were always happy to clarify

How Things Work

Appliances & Manuals

Instruction manuals for the airconditioning, oven, dishwasher, and other appliances are located in the bottom drawer in the kitchen.

If you have any questions or would like assistance, just let us know were happy to help.

Coffee & Comfort

A coffee pod machine is available for your use, along with tea and basic supplies.

  • Compatible pods: Nespresso
  • Please switch the machine off after use

If anything runs low during your stay, just let us know.

Smart TV & Streaming

The Smart TV is set up with the following apps:

  • Netflix
  • Prime Video
  • Disney+
  • Hayu

Youre welcome to log in using your own accounts.

We recommend logging out before departure though well also doublecheck this before the next guest arrives.

AirConditioning & Remotes

Airconditioning is available for both the bedroom and living area.

  • Remotes are provided in their respective rooms
  • Please switch units off when not in use

If youre unsure how anything works, were happy to help.

Yoga & Slow Mornings

Yoga mats are provided if you feel like stretching, enjoying a quiet morning practice, or if youve forgotten yours and are heading to a local class.

A simple local favourite:

  • Early morning beach walk (sunrise over Point Cartwright)
  • Coffee or juice afterwards

Nearby Essentials

Security & Keys

  • If youd like to lock the green door when you go out, you can.
  • Your key set includes an additional key if youd like to lock the screen door.
  • The screen door can be locked from the inside for extra peace of mind.
  • You also have a garage door buzzer.
  • If youd like to lock the green door when you go out, you can use your key.
  • A garage door buzzer is also provided.

If you have any questions about access or keys, let us know.

Safety & Practical Info

  • Emergency services: 000
  • First aid supplies are located above the fridge.
  • Fire safety information is on the top shelf of the pantry.
  • Rubbish & recycling are beside the fridge (big bin = rubbish, small bin = recycling).

Rubbish & Recycling

Bins are located beside the fridge.

  • The big bin is for rubbish
  • The small bin is for recycling

Please empty into the outdoor bins located halfway up the driveway beside Unit 10.

Before You Go

Before heading off, we kindly ask that you:

  • Leave the kitchen generally tidy
  • Wipe down benches after use
  • Place all rubbish in the bins located halfway up the driveway beside Unit 10
  • Leave used linen and towels in the sink beside the washing machine
  • Switch off lights and airconditioning

On your way out: simply turn the small lock on the door handle the door will close behind you and lock automatically.

Thank you we really appreciate it.

Feedback

After checkout, Airbnb will invite you to leave a review.

If youd like to share your experience, it genuinely helps especially as a small, thoughtfully run stay. And if anything during your visit could have been better, wed always appreciate hearing directly from you as well.

A Final Note

We hope your stay has been calm, comfortable, and restorative.

If you need anything at all during your stay whether its a question, a local recommendation, or help with the space please dont hesitate to reach out.

Were nearby and happy to help where we can. Safe travels.
